        "username": "maloo",
        "tags": [
          "SERVICE_USER"
        ]
      },
      "date": "2012-12-08 11:02:44.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.3/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/13cb2038-4121-11e2-a719-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
